==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rsum
<hw>R⟦eacute⟧`su"m⟦eacute⟧"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[F. See <er>Resume</er>.]</ety> <def>A summing up; a condensed
statement; an abridgment or brief recapitulation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The exellent little <qex>r⟦eacute⟧sum⟦eacute⟧</qex> thereof in Dr.
Landsborough's book.</q> <rj><qau>C. Kingsley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A brief summary of the education, experience,
accomplishments, and other professional qualifications of a person, such
as that prepared by one applying for a job.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Resume</ent>⟦br⟧
